p.k: Short, Drama Spain (2015). Hrají: Hammudi Al-Rahmoun Font, Laia Costa. Režie: Laura Jou.
p.d: Laura and Luis. Two characters mired in a contradiction : she wants to go with him but attacks and despises him and he does not want her back but there he is, at home and taking off his jacket ... The story of heartbreak in which a woman confuse desire with the need to fill an infinite void.
